data.description: Open House this Sunday, October 8th from 11 am to 3 pm! This beautiful home is the definition of MOVE-IN READY! From the gravel driveway and automatic gate, to the massive storage shed and children's playscape in a Texas Sized Backyard all wrapped in a privacy fence anchored down with metal poles and stained for maximum use. If you like the outside of the home just wait till you experience the inside. This 2019 build has been very well taken care of and has many upgrades. The Water Softener, Refrigerator, Brand New Dishwasher, and even the Washer and Dryer will be staying with the home. Lots of great natural light, great sized bedrooms, and a separate tub and shower in the master bath. This home will be wonderful for many years to come!
